  "time_ut": 1662008961,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dad \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0d8b\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dae\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Efforts to recover the payment for the Chinese fertilizer ship have been unsuccessful",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Agriculture, Wildlife and Forestry, Mr. Mahinda Amaraweera said in the Parliament today (1) that the 6.9 million dollars paid to the Chinese fertilizer ship or the attempts made to get chemical fertilizers instead have failed.",
        "The Minister of Agriculture said that the Attorney General has been consulted on the steps to be taken in this regard and action will be taken soon.",
        "The Minister said that an expert committee headed by the Secretary of the Ministry of Agriculture has been appointed to look into this issue further and come up with solutions.",
        "The Minister of Agriculture said this while replying to a question raised by Athuraliye Ratana Thero, a member of our People's Power Party."
      ],
